description:
Your dream wardrobe is just one tap away – discover an online shop with an impressive variety of fashion, beauty and home products and brands, available anywhere and anytime.  

Download the Fashion Days app so you can:

•Shop your favorite brands’ latest collections and find special offers;
•Never miss a sale: you will receive real-time alerts about campaigns kick-off and special promotions;
•Enjoy high-quality full-screen product images and 360° product videos, because every detail matters;
•Filter your unlimited options: narrow down your search by brand, product category, size, price or color;
•Pay with a single-step checkout: you've got secure credit card payment option;
•Save all of your most-wanted items in the Wishlist;
•Get easy breezy access to your account (settings, orders, addresses, vouchers & more);
•Get in-app notifications about the latest collections, trends and special prices.

Fashion Days is the one-stop online destination that offers shopping and inspiration to over 1,500,000 customers in Romania, Bulgaria and Hungary.  Here you can find clothing, footwear and accessories for women, men and children from top brands: Calvin Klein, Converse, Diesel, Esprit, Fossil, GAP, Guess, Karl Lagerfeld, Liu Jo, Love Moschino, Mango, New Balance, Nike, Pepe Jeans London, Puma, Skechers, Tommy Hilfiger, U.S. Polo Assn., UGG, Under Armour, Ted Baker, Gant, Emporio Armani, Timberland, Napapijri, Furla, adidas and many more.  

Your feedback is pure gold for us, so we would be more than happy to hear about your shopping experience with the Fashion Days app. An email with your feedback and suggestions at info@fashiondays.ro will be more than appreciated.
